- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper discusses the performance of dialog models equipped with OOD detection mechanisms. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is relevant as the paper deals with neural dialog models. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the release of new dialog datasets.
